    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now let's get started!</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> to a heatproof bowl, then cover the bowl with <strong>cling film</strong> and pierce a few holes in the top with a fork</p><p>Put the bowl in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 6-8 min<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>or until the potatoes are fork-tender</p><p>Chop your <strong>brown onion[s] </strong>into thin wedges</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1693826042988-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
