    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are fork-tender, crush them lightly with a fork in the bowl – these are your <strong>crushed potatoes</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>crushed potatoes</strong> to the pan with your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>,<strong> </strong>a small knob of <strong>butter </strong>and your <strong>dried thyme</strong> and<strong> </strong>give everything a good mix up</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1 min or until the butter has melted</p>",
