      "instruction": "<p>Top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong> and cook, covered, for 2 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>one-pan Alpine-style sausage & waxy potato hash</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> to the <strong>mustard</strong> <strong>dressing</strong> and toss – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
